aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 34校網掛？"},{"pid":"a8313c8ff01765b250a18f588f08d350e6b8b0a7","tid":2408960,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"呎價三萬元應該毫無懸念"},{"pid":"b69404fb66a889452c904b30e35e4bbcc33a1082","tid":2408960,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔話自己係加多利山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e3ab79fbbbd945ad9da0c3a1a9ce561e9f2552","tid":2408960,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"雷霆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db123821ac5740e3865d526660234ea18236939","tid":2408960,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"果度都叫何文田？"},{"pid":"ce33f873f956f15e84dfc196b48d14f187d823a0","tid":2408960,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69404fb66a889452c904b30e35e4bbcc33a1082","tid":2408960,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔話自己係加多利山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"加多利山應該賣貴過何文田"},{"pid":"94fee036b0612ce608d4a9f1938fedc8a6eb132a","tid":2408960,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"何文田的傳統範圍僅為加多利山（古稱大石鼓）、十二號山（古稱紅磡山）及採石山之間的谷地（包括今日已不屬何文田的染布房街與彌敦道之間的旺角地域），即現今亞皆老街以南一段的窩打老道沿線兩旁的地區，而該範圍之東南的小丘，則因何文田的地名而被命名為何文田山（即何文田街及何文田山道一帶）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了上述範圍外，隨著社區發展，原本不在何文田範圍的公共設施，亦以「何文田」命名。戰後香港政府於何文田山以東南（即公主道的東邊）採石山興建一廉租屋邨，命名為何文田邨，原本在紅磡區的採石山與十二號山之間佛光街一帶因而被視為「何文田」的一部分。後來愛民邨及山谷道邨分別於十二號山及老龍坑北部落成，「何文田」的區域更延伸到這些地方，採石山、十二號山及老龍坑等地名漸漸為人淡忘。"},{"pid":"a76bc15bfeaaaf6c3690726fe74b5274f9bd3169","tid":2408960,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"參考返匯璽個價差唔多？"},{"pid":"d032dcb671b7a76fe8ea26f8562b7e060f656b08","tid":2408960,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"其實何文田好撚大下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太子道西、阿皆老街、窩打老道等等"},{"pid":"668ac1ad1523c5aa9e8ee8fafea33838b126664d","tid":2408960,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a76bc15bfeaaaf6c3690726fe74b5274f9bd3169","tid":2408960,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"參考返匯璽個價差唔多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"開細則個呎價應該會攞到好盡<br />\n我估1房都要10球"},{"pid":"704b4729aed0eaecfca3a6903a2525bee3831e5b","tid":2408960,"uid":171611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"仲起咁多開放式做乜尻"},{"pid":"0286c6ac22d08a3acd85560212f64701280d17ef","tid":2408960,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"佢隔離d太子道西舊樓全部千鳩幾呎..."},{"pid":"8b74d4ae0eea9a38874663ddabee4346f669bfaf","tid":2408960,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0286c6ac22d08a3acd85560212f64701280d17ef","tid":2408960,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"佢隔離d太子道西舊樓全部千鳩幾呎..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f083634ba70c1292acbaeb0b5c88446d84e61fe8","tid":2408960,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"行幾步就係新世紀廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b205a1edd4dd3f1537ca30f369c841a7be4db